# SampleUISystem

## Purpose
Drives the SandboxApp scene. Guards on ResourceMapSingletonComponent and
SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent presence; returns early until both are available.

First productive frame: creates the scene camera (1280x720, ReactsToInput=true), initializes
SampleUISingletonComponent with hard-coded starting values from the config, and emits a
LoadLayoutEvent to load SandboxUI.json.

Every subsequent frame: emits in-frame draw events for a flat quad, a sprite (matched to a UI
entity by UUID), a static multi-line text string, and an animated elapsed-time clock string.
Also renders an ImGui "Settings" panel exposing live editing of quad and text transforms.

## Input Components
| Component | Access |
|---|---|
| SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent | read |
| ResourceMapSingletonComponent | read |
| BaseComponent | read |
| ImageComponent | read |
| TextComponent | read |
| SampleUISingletonComponent | write |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SampleUISingletonComponent | write / add (deferred) | Created on first productive frame; mutable scene state editable via ImGui |
| OrthographicCameraComponent | add (deferred) | Created on first productive frame; 1280x720, ReactsToInput=true |
| LoadLayoutEvent | add (deferred) | Emitted once on first productive frame to trigger loading SandboxUI.json |
| DrawQuadInFrameEvent | add (inframe) | One flat coloured quad per frame |
| DrawSpriteInFrameEvent | add (inframe) | One sprite per frame; entity matched by UUID against SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent.m_UUIDUI1 |
| DrawStringInFrameEvent | add (inframe) | Two text strings per frame: static multi-line text and animated elapsed-time clock |
